Now, the fix: in the STAR case, when ignoreStar is true, we need to set ignoreStar = false after ignoring the star. The code becomes:
```
case STAR:
  if (ignoreStar) {
    // Mark the position after the star as the new start of the line.
    ignoreStar = false; // add this
  } else {
    // The star is part of the comment.
    if (builder.length() > 0) {
      builder.append(' ');
    }
    builder.append('*');
  }
  token = next();
  continue;
```

